{"tid":1411455,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民間記者會要小心呢啲問題！","createTime":"2019-08-05T03:44:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T13:15:34.000Z","uid":152594,"like":88,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"b743e15c5b651650500da6a984da6efc222192e2","tid":1411455,"uid":152594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:44:34.000Z","msg":"關於搞民間記者會呢幾樣野大家應該要留意下<br />\n<br />\n首先，亦都係最重要，就係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔可以打反擊</span></span><br />\n即係唔可以佢記者會講咗乜，我地逐點澄清fact check<br />\n因為咁樣做都係會令佢地嘅agenda得到曝光同討論度<br />\n唔好否認、澄清︰「今日呢單新聞關於xxx係假，實際上事實上yyyy」<br />\n而係直接陳述事實︰「今日發生一件事件係關於yyyy」<br />\n<br />\n對付fake news一個好方法就係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">直接攻擊源頭</span></span></strong><br />\n同大家講，呢篇新聞嘅源頭不可信，所以呢篇野係fake news<br />\n同理，我地都要話俾所有人知，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政府記者會不可信</span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n同時統一搞記者會，就<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有成為大台嘅潛在風險</span></strong></span><br />\n不論係泛民定本土定連登巴絲定前線<br />\n邊個搞到好，就算我地唔當係，政府都會將佢變成大台<br />\n因為咁先有個靶俾佢地打<br />\n所以搞一個formal嘅民間記者會要仔細諗清楚<br />\n希望大家可以集思廣益，諗下有冇方法冇大台嘅同時拆解政府記者會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港　時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"473827cc871248dad77c828234e8a1bc91fed891","tid":1411455,"uid":152594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:44:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ac9ef27b75ca11b0bcf35f132c1bcdcf143bef","tid":1411455,"uid":152594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:45:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b5caefb6b933553f88905421cbd99261f